{"tid":280181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖遊記］關西，獨遊，拉麵，行山，漫步之行","createTime":"2017-06-12T01:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T14:21:49.000Z","uid":65708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c288deb9257b8f9fad2ea46137934bee449f72","tid":280181,"uid":65708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:46:45.000Z","msg":"HI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近年有部份航空公司推出嘅香港去關西機場嘅機票都唔係好貴，又見唔少人都去完關西都話唔錯，就趁五月下旬關西天氣未算開始熱時獨遊玩下，結果去完覺得關西確係幾正，所以就打痕寫篇遊歷，亦都俾黎緊想去嘅巴絲睇下有無野值得參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實呢次係我第三次去日本，但呢篇係我第一篇遊記，如果反應ＯＫ的話，就寫埋另外兩次遊日之旅，分別係「關東富士山之行」同「鹿兒島櫻島屋久島種子島之行」，因為適逢又就到富士山開山之時，或姐可以俾有興趣嘅巴絲做微微嘅參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似寫左好多無謂野.....好！去片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行程：<br />\n23/5 (二) 黃昏落機，夜遊難波，道頓堀<br />\n24/5 (三) 奈良，稻荷，通天閣夜景<br />\n25/5 (四) 京都，鞍馬寺，貴船神社，嵐山，八坂神社，祇園花見小路<br />\n26/5 (五) 大阪城，天王寺動物園，回氣之日<br />\n27/5 (六) 金剛山，河內天野天野酒莊，黑門市場<br />\n28/5 (日) 黑潮市場，和歌山城，Rinku Premium Outlets，訓機場<br />\n29/5 (一) 早機回港<br />\n<br />\n第一日(23/5)：<br />\n<br />\n搭香港航空 HX 632 香港時間1250起飛，日本時間1805抵達，機程順暢無阻，甫落機拎返埋托運嘅大背囊就去機場一樓嘅關西旅遊訊息服務中心(KTIC)買京阪一日觀光券FOR 25/5 京都日使用，盛惠1200YEN<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.keihan.co.jp/travel/tw/tickets/special-osaka\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keihan.co.jp%2Ftravel%2Ftw%2Ftickets%2Fspecial-osaka&d=y2jl%2FZ68RTx3bFOKJOsQFP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e87207e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.keihan.co.jp/travel/tw/tickets/special-osaka</a><br />\n<br />\n買完之後就上返機場二樓經天橋過去對面嘅鐵路大樓入面嘅「JR窗口」(一間綠色嘅服務中心)買ICOCA+HARUKA車飛，因為呢次行程頭五晚都係住浪速區嘅一間HOSTEL，所以就買左去天王寺嘅單程車飛，兩者加埋盛惠3100YEN，其中有2000YEN係ICOCA卡嘅儲值額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢期賣緊小飛俠嘅限量特別版，都幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VSPd0Sb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVSPd0Sb.jpg&h=95397c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞掂哂之後就用乘換案內APPS睇下幾時有車<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vtJ4VUf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvtJ4VUf.jpg&h=236892ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n慢慢入埋閘行過去上車無幾耐就開車了，而且比本身嘅PLANNING仲要早左一班上到車，爽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準時1918落車，但唔係先去HOSTEL，而係去天王寺站嘅MIO SHOPPING MALL內嘅MONT-BELL行山店逛下先，點解？因為日本嘅行山店實在太吸引了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KWDruCy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKWDruCy.jpg&h=38172107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n逛完之後就由天王寺站行去HOSTEL<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/yD1KlCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyD1KlCd.jpg&h=a8a966af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻貓神奇地會o係幾日後另一個位置再同我相遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/R4jDuhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FR4jDuhj.jpg&h=8085f7b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行左大約15分鐘左右就到HOSTEL了，都係我黎緊5晚嘅住宿點，每晚80 HKD，雖然唔夠傳說中嘅鑽石酒店平但都好便宜啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gaEahp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgaEahp2.jpg&h=65b03c51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且或姐因為係3月先開嘅關係，所以內部都好新淨企理<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zskjOz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzskjOz8.jpg&h=1bed62aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gp2WL4X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fgp2WL4X.jpg&h=18cfe7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過床位空間就唔算大，只有1米 X 1米 X 2米左右，但床頭都設有燈同電制<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/onU6vo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FonU6vo9.jpg&h=3b70f2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地下大廳係公共空間，有免費零食提供<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OZiHWTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOZiHWTg.jpg&h=c0f4d8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MhGfgtp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMhGfgtp.jpg&h=ff29d0f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安置哂D行李之後，就出去搵野食<br />\n最後入左一間叫「きりん寺 大阪総本店」嘅麵店食晚飯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PYMZS1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPYMZS1n.jpg&h=a0e5dec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n座低之後就去買麵票，俾票後等左十分鐘左右就有野食了，食法好似係將枱上面嘅油同醋按個人口味撈埋入碗麵到一齊食<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SDalgaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSDalgaR.jpg&h=33630f9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味道都OK嘅，惹味，成碗麵都滑滑地咁，盛惠970 YEN<br />\n<br />\n食完野睇下時間都係去到20:30左右，仍然好早，所以就係附近隨便散下步同行去道頓堀<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ohUwYUx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FohUwYUx.jpg&h=6c2d3b34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Sz1A9fR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSz1A9fR.jpg&h=7c33aded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一夜待續..."},{"pid":"12bea7f2e8644d3582b876a7ee00f68633ee3712","tid":280181,"uid":44833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:02:42.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e606d0dd8dfc63f23f22c2cae44bccbbd179c5","tid":280181,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:12:05.000Z","msg":"今時今日香港人出關西旅遊post真係公廁咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c13500d84ff247e6567115745cab9b7e7e8f3d","tid":280181,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:13:01.000Z","msg":"飛田新地遊記呢"},{"pid":"8d25d3e3b58fb65e89b32b6414c60889f53c2b70","tid":280181,"uid":118746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T08:27:23.000Z","msg":"劉明等啊等"},{"pid":"182f2928039f62c002f00531808959e3713d4b24","tid":280181,"uid":65708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T14:21:49.000Z","msg":"SORRY....我發覺我開錯台了，本來係想開O係旅遊台，呢個POST由佢沉吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新POST LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/281213/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/281213/page/1</a>"}]}